data.description: When you step inside this spacious 2,130 square-foot home, boasting 2 bedrooms (flex room can be turned back into a 3rd bedroom), 2.5 baths, you’ll be immediately captivated by the vaulted ceilings and views out to the pool. The versatile great room, originally designed as a 3rd bedroom, offers flexibility as a den or an entertainment space. Situated on an expansive plot spanning three lots (.69 acres), this home has undergone a series of thoughtful updates. Plank floor tile throughout the entire home, BRAND NEW 2023 ROOF, custom board and batten design, and modern light fixtures. You'll appreciate the convenience of a complete home R/O water filtration system. Home has an attached two car garage with epoxy floors and a split unit ac. Septic just pumped and inspected. Extend your entertainment space with a covered 26x6 outdoor area with a custom tongue and groove wood plank ceiling. An outdoor half-bath adds convenience for your guests. The detached 40x50 aluminum garage with three bays, including a finished living space with air conditioning, perfect for a personal business office or guest quarters. Complete with a kitchenette and Split Ac Unit.
